Interface BEModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BEModelImpl

    public interface BEModel
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'BE Model'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Dbt
    • Name
    • Component List
    • Requirement List
    • Formula List
    • Import

    See Also:
    BehaviortreePackage.getBEModel()
